<br>
 One year after the open of the nexus portals. In a Tavern in Shar Vahl, and Bard Tells tales of The Stormligers, And an outlander asked him what a Stormliger was, this is his reply.<br>
<br>
       According to Vah Shir legend an individual that has been give great a great gift by the spirits is born every generation. This individual may or may not know of this gift, but some learn of it and learn to use it. These individuals can either bring order to chaos, or chaos to order. It all depends on what their destiny holds for them. These individuals are called Stormligers.  They come from all classes of the Vah Shir race. Stormligers all bear lighting bolt markings some where on there body. They all have one thing in common, a unnatural feel to the air around them.  Stormligers of order,the air around them is calm and un moving like the calm before a storm, no matter how strong the wind around them blows they are unaffected by it.  The signs that one is a stormliger of order is that the individual is of a kind,loyal and noble nature and that their fur never moves when the wind blows through it.  Stormligers of chaos, The air around them is always in turmoil, and there is the sensation of an electric tingle, like lighting is going to strike. If a Stormliger is angered the electric sensation intensifies greatly.  These individuals are spiteful and filled with anger and hate. they enjoy causing pain, suffering and strife where ever they go. Those my friend are Stormligers, and it has been said that once in a great many generations several stormligers are born, but there is no knowlege of this ever happening. There have been several prophecies of a Stormliger that will both bring order to chaos and chaos to order, but that is another story altogether. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/belvenelite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=tigonstormliger>Tigon Stormliger</A> at: 5/8/03 11:14:04 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#AB8C5B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/belvenelite.showUserPublicProfile?gid=blackarrachnea>Blackarrachnea</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Newbie</span><br